<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90cbcc22-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s6964"><num value="6964">§ 6964.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated for fiscal year 2001, and each fiscal year thereafter, such sums as may be necessary for the Task Force to carry out the functions described in <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s6962">section 6962 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id90cbcc23-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/106/286/dB/tV/s504">Pub. L. 106–286, div. B, title V, § 504</ref>, <date date="2000-10-10">Oct. 10, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/904">114 Stat. 904</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
